Subject: Server not upgrading
Description: I have tried to upgrade our server from version 5.9.4.0 to 5.9.4.1 but it stays on 5.9.4.0. I've tried to apply the update immediately and schedule it, but neither works. We would like to get it upgraded due to the ADV-2025-001 advisory.
What_We_Know__c:
the patch did not apply, my guess is that it was checked before re-adding the patch to the live server and thus it did not find the correct path.
after another check it worked
Next_Steps__c: closing as the patch applied correctly and the customer confirmed
